data.description: Back on market due to no fault of the seller! This 3 BDRM, 3 BATH, end unit townhouse is nestled on a corner lot of the Tide Water Cove neighborhood!  It is filled with tons of natural light, open concept family room with fireplace, the kitchen has stained cabinetry, pantry, an eat in kitchen area, and a view to the formal dining room with entry to the backyard, and includes all appliances. This home has spacious bedrooms and owner's suite with bonus nursery or office, the master bath showcases a double vanity, tub and shower combo and two walk-in closets. This floor plan makes the most out of every space in the home.  Tide Water Cove is just a short walk to Lake Lanier the marina and Fish Tales Lakeside Grill! This neighborhood is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, and many outdoor activities. You don't want to miss out on this great property! This home is sold AS-IS and ready for move in!!  Great neutral paint colors and NEW carpet installed the first of December.
